data.description: Welcome Home! The rocking chair front porch welcomes you as you enter this adorable 3 bed, 2 bath ranch situated on a large corner lot. The interior boasts updated paint, LVT flooring, spacious rooms & a very functional layout. There is a wood burning fireplace in the family room that opens to the kitchen with white cabinets, subway tile backsplash, and stainless appliances. The stained back deck overlooks an over-sized yard that is fully fenced in. There is a well on the property that can be used to water the lawn & more! The house is connected to public water and sewer. Located on a large corner lot with ease of access to Lexington and interstates. No HOA! Motivated Seller! Call for questions!
